{"tid":2004632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Project Veritas踢爆CBS(美國民主黨黨媒之一)請演員扮病人排隊作假新聞","createTime":"2020-05-06T14:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T15:35:09.000Z","uid":62151,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e86c066f269d11b8beb98b6b6079594d39cbd1d4","tid":2004632,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T14:33:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">如果你唔知Project Veritas 係咩黎&darr;<br />\nProject Veritas 係一個專門透過内幕人士比料,再用偷拍等手法將真相公諸於世嘅組織<br />\n踢爆過嘅事有好多,例如政治審查,假新聞,政治宣傳,貪腐等等<br />\n<br />\n呢次佢地踢爆嘅係CBS(美國民主黨黨媒之一)<br />\n透過請災難演員<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(作假新聞專用演員)</span>扮病人係醫院扮隊<br />\n<br />\n内幕人士踢爆搵演員排隊&darr;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZLGZB8Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZLGZB8Q.png&h=b2e81840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來一早有曬時間表&darr;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CmPgEov.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCmPgEov.png&h=88c617fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請&quot;義工&quot;作新聞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GwyQJSi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGwyQJSi.png&h=c6e073e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫&quot;假病人&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8YWrhcU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8YWrhcU.png&h=6a06872b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫護承認有假病人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p431Qyp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp431Qyp.png&h=2959f17a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位要明白,左仔假新聞唔係香港先有<br />\n最衰係乜?CBS呢一類假新聞同WHO一樣會被youtube定性做&quot;權威消息&quot;<br />\n之後就會用黎打壓異見聲音同埋沒真相<br />\n所以點解絕對言論自由咁重要,就係為左要抗衡呢啲野<br />\n<br />\n詳情請睇原片(全英文)：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oQWRCECbN-Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoQWRCECbN-Y&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBad04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=42ecfa5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oQWRCECbN-Y</a></span>"},{"pid":"102918be51e4ab91dd1cea1881d83d4aa85b54d1","tid":2004632,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T14:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4255b01a79b4034a32890cb54625f5257107c33","tid":2004632,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T14:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca41775bc65f1b0ba49c202e6b91d8a113d5cd9","tid":2004632,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T14:44:52.000Z","msg":"侵: you are fake news !!!"},{"pid":"499db43fb50c29f87c24cad77e113bbf50e5d2f9","tid":2004632,"uid":98289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:35:09.000Z","msg":"咁佢地都好有計劃去做假新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}